The trolley spirometer market is regulated by various government authorities such as the FDA in the US and the European Medicines Agency in Europe.

10. What are the different types of trolley spirometers available in the market?
There are primarily two types of trolley spirometers available in the market: volume-based spirometers and flow-based spirometers.

